rComments: Exceptional orator and general muse to all that are interested in philosophical reflection and discovery.  The student should expect to work hard for a good mark.  The prof really tries to help with any issues and is very approachable.

Newly minted as a professor- and well deserved in all respects. She is a great orator, brings in a certain style and rhetoric to what can be a dull topic/readings. Extremely approachable and kind, one of the best professors I have had in my undergrad. Plus- her style is as chic and lovely as she in.

She was really cool, was interested in the material, and was really halpful. Nice and easy going. She encouraged discussion and really made learning the material easier. She is a good lecturer and does a great job as a prof overall. She also has a great sense of style. A positive learning expereince.
